The package consists of the following files

1.AirLine.war
2.airreservationsystem .sql
3.readme

Running Instructions
-----------------------

1. Create a database AIRRESERVATIONSYSTEM
   run the sql script "airreservationsystem .sql"

2. Deploy the war file in the webapps folder of tomcat

3. start tomcat container 

4. Open the browser and type in the 
   http://localhost:8080/AirLine/Index.html
   
Note:
    Database requires password 
